title: The Long Dark v1 16 Rugged Sentinel-RELOADED
description:
The Long Dark is a thoughtful, exploration-survival experience that
  challenges solo players to think for themselves as they explore an expansive
  frozen wilderness in the aftermath of a geomagnetic disaster.
  There are no zombies -- only you, the cold, and all the threats Mother Nature
  can muster.
